⍝ Reciprocal.tc
⍝ ═════════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: B and Z numeric nonzero
      ⍝ inv: ÷B ←→ 1÷B
      B ← 0.5+|⎕RVAL 1 (,5) (,0 0 1 0 0)     ⍝ nonzero positive reals
      (÷B) ≡ 1÷B
1
      B ← ⎕RVAL 1 (,4) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      B ← B+(B=0)                              ⍝ avoid zero
      (÷B) ≡ 1÷B
1
